[I] A JSON implementation in C

[T] JSON-C implements a reference counting object model that allows you to
[T] easily construct JSON objects in C, output them as JSON formatted strings
[T] and parse JSON formatted strings back into the C representation of JSON
[T] objects.

[U] https://github.com/json-c/json-c/wiki

